Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的存在感越来越薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是空气一般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一开始便不存在于这世上一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确确实实地渐渐迎来终结之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该说些什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该怎么回答好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时真是开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经晚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过当时要是再多去几个地方就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量留下回忆吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是以前的我大概会这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「真不像你的作风啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 由梦 有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为有事才来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天放学后我们去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约 约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言 对由梦而言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能成为一个美好的回忆的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会 吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥很寂寞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子 一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的 我不想后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以… 再见了呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早饭做好了 快点过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 你这一言不发的是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那你快点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约会我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是阴天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 放学后会是个适合约会的好天气的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？ 但是天气预报说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的肯定没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过天气预报也不怎么靠得住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？ 你一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们就一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有东西忘带了必须回去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外 完全看不出你是会忘带东西的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们就先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别迟到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是这么一回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我心里也明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我们现在就去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（此店出租）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近 要是再有点好玩的地方就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影院穿校服是进不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点什么的无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很有约会的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我的艺术品被
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,p i ne a pp le （菠萝）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ch o co l a te （巧克力）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输的人请吃饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 别擅自决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备 石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么认真是在许什么愿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密 说了就没法实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你不许什么愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们去下个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃 巧克力香蕉不管吃多少次也不会腻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 搭配得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话虽如此 也只不过是把巧克力覆盖在了香蕉上而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样没有意义的闲逛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我不是说了嘛 地点无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 约会不是一般都要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是水族馆之类的更热闹的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去也不晚 我们去樱花公园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的并不是去哪 而是身边有哥哥你在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到哥哥的嘴里会说出约会两字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不行哦 我很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 天晴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 跟由梦说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运 是无法改变的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 哥哥 来这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃课来约会 姐姐知道的话要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姐的话 已经被她察觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去后不知道会不会被训呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没办法呢 创造了那么多快乐的回忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之下 被训几句也不算什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.76,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后再陪我去一个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 在梦里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然时间很短
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像今天这样 一直都像是梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以预见到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过预知梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得太唐突了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始 还觉得不会是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我的梦一定会变成现实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后哥哥会消失的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从梦到哥哥消失那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我的愿望不会被实现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为哥哥 会从我身边消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:13:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再在我面前欢笑的原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直喜欢哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直装作若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提醒着自己不能忘记妹妹的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法坦率面对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易忍到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直欺骗自己到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为快乐的时光越多 离别就越伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 还是做不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我就是这么喜欢哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 喜欢你 好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论说多少遍都不够
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 梦会醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以… 再见了呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 去姐姐那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着还残留着关于哥哥的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐她一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 去姐姐那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着还残留着关于哥哥的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花 已经凋零了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以前整年都盛开着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有机会再看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能稍微 和我说会儿话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你有时间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道我还剩下多少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能你无法相信我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我是正义的魔法使哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护这座岛的 正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 好像一点也不惊讶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是不相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不相信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾有一个无论如何都想用魔法去拯救的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有努力学习过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厚厚的魔法书都读了几十本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连熬了几天的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一定 会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定可以救到那个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管再怎么看书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使想破脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是找不到办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然能够救助岛上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我最想救的人却
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救我一直努力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要忘记弟弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要和弟弟君一直一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是那么喜欢弟弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比谁都重要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对绝对不要分开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没有解救的办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有弟弟君的话 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会活不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法一个人活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.82,0:21:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.92,0:21:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要丢下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好永远都要在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好永远都要一心同体的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再生你气了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再勉强你系领子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟君…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:22:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法的力量到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键时候根本派不上用场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种没用的力量我不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.65,0:23:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把弟弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我最重要的人还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.96,0:25:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦的重奏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.96,0:25:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}Da Capo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.93,0:25:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是重复的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.03,0:25:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的 回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:21.31,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}泣かぬように　笑ってみた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:27.19,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}僕たちは何処へ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:40.79,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}星のない空を見上げ　願うように息をした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:51.65,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}想うほどにくり返してく　痛みの中で...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:08:09.70,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}続く未知を呼び覚ます　愛を君に送るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:18.79,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}明日が涙に濡れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:25.86,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}桜ヒラリ　夢の音ユラリ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:30.78,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}優しく導く　その声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:43.21,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}いつまでも心の奥　枯れない記憶になる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:59.76,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}傷痕を隠すように　歌ってたあの頃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:07.19,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}君はただ何も言わず
